  "title": "`connectStateResults.searchResults` should be of nullable type",
  "body": "## 🐛 Bug description\r\n\r\nCurrently `searchResults` is of type `SearchResults<BasicDoc>` but on component initialization using `connectStateResults` HOC, the value is `null` until Algolia's first response. So in reality it's a nullable prop and should be of type `SearchResults<BasicDoc> | null`.",
